document_data.History:
Freona's tea house was one of the most famous places in Phlan in [[1489 DR]].

After [[Vorgansharax]]'s coup, she hid in her shop many individuals sought after by the [[Tears of Virulence]].{{Cite adventurers league/Escape from Phlan|7}}

For this, the dragon ordered the tea house to be burned down, but an adventuring party hired by the resistance managed to help Freona to escape from the city.{{Cite adventurers league/Escape from Phlan|11-17}}
